videos.description: Tulsa QB Seth Boomer connects with a wide-open Keenen Johnson for a 33-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tulsa's Boomer throws 33-yard TD

videos.description: Houston QB D'Eriq King scrambles and finds Keith Corbin who leaps over two defenders and scores a 32-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Corbin leaps and scores 32-yard TD

videos.description: Early in the second, Houston turns the ball over twice, while Tulsa turns it over once, in a two-in-a-half minute span.
videos.headline: Tulsa Boomer and Houston King exchange turnovers

videos.description: D'Eriq King looks to pass, but finds a seam and runs in for 19-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: King  bursts for a 19-yard TD

videos.description: Tulsa RB Corey Taylor II gets the handoff and runs in for and 8-yard touchdown to the Trojans up 23-17.
videos.headline: Taylor punches in an 8-yard TD

videos.description: On a quarterback draw, D'Eriq King runs in for a 61-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: King erupts for 61-yard TD

videos.description: Houston fakes run, then QB D'Eric King floats a pass to Romello Brooker for a 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Houston's Brooker scores 9-yard TD

videos.description: D'Eric King finds Marquez Stevenson in the end zone for a 6-yard touchdown to put the Cougars up 41-26.
videos.headline: King's 5th TD seals Houston's win
